AND THAT'S WHY YOU

CINCO DE MAYO

NOOB NOG, LEETMAS WAS BORN."

ALWAYS SO BUSY

ALL RIGHT,
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

WHAT TIME--
WHAT TIME IS THE RACE?

YEAH, I'M GONNA BE
LATE FOR THAT.

WHAT ABOUT MY PIE?

YEAH, SURE.

YOU GUYS AT THE RACE.

OH, I GOT ONE!
HELLO, BRIAN,
I LOVE YOU!

- YOU JUST
COMPLIMENTED HIM.

OH, WAIT.
I MEAN, I DON'T KNOW.

I MEAN, YES, BRIAN,
I HATE YOU!

I DIDN'T MEAN IT!
I MEAN, I DIDN'T--!

I MEAN DON'T
COME BACK! BRIAN!

IS THERE

TELL THE OTHER GIRLS!

RUN!

I DON'T NEED
ANYTHING FROM ANYBODY.

HA HA HA! YEAH,

- I GOTTA GET THIS
BIRD IN THE OVEN.
- BRIAN!

TWO O'CLOCK.
WEAR BLACK AND SATIN SPATS.

AN UNAUTHORIZED TURKEY

CONTEST OR...?

TELL ME ABOUT
WHAT WENT DOWN

A STORY ALL RIGHT.

IT'S THE STORY OF
AN FPS WUNDERKIND,

FRAMED FOR A CRIME
HE DIDN'T COMMIT

IT'S THE STORY OF A SCHOOL
THAT TURNED THEIR BACKS ON ME

AND ONCE I GET MY HANDS
ON THAT EVIDENCE,

IT'S GONNA BE THE STORY
OF MY REDEMPTION.

THAT SOUNDS LIKE
A STORY THE REAL SHOTBOT

FAT CHANCE, DOLL FACE.
THE LAW RIDES ALONE.

I SEE.
THAT SOUNDS VERY LONELY.

WHY DO YOU WANT
TO HELP ME, ANYWAY?

BECAUSE YOU'RE NOT
THE ONLY ONE LOOKING
FOR A SECOND CHANCE.

MAYBE... MAKE OUT
AND TOUCH A BUNCH

WHO KNOWS? LET'S SEE
WHERE THE WIND BLOWS.

HEY, GET BACK TO WORK,
BRIAN.

EXTRA WHIP ON ME!
ALL RIGHT! YEAH! WHOO!

I PROMISE.

ALL RIGHT, HERE'S THE PLAN.

400 REPS ON THIS THING,

MEET SHANE AND SQUEEZE HIM UP.

HYDROGEN AND OXYGEN.

CIDER TONIGHT?

DEAN'S GONNA KILL ME!

THE RACE IS
NOT GONNA START
ANY YEAR NOW!

EXTRA WHIP ON ME, OKAY?

YEAH, WELL,
THEY WERE OUT OF DECAF,

WELL, LOOKS LIKE

SO, LAW, ONCE YOU'VE

PROBABLY BECOME
RICH AND FAMOUS AGAIN.

WHEN THAT HAPPENS,

DON'T EXPECT ME TO,
LIKE, CARE ABOUT YOU

MY OTHER SCHOOL
SAID I WAS SO WEIRD

AND THEY WERE GOING
TO DEACTIVATE ME.

YOUR SCHOOL
SOUNDS LIKE MY DAD,

YOUR SCHOOL DOESN'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S TALKING ABOUT.

YOUR SCHOOL
SHOULD HAVE LEFT MOM
A LONG TIME AGO!

NO ONE'S EVER LEFT ME
THAT COMMENT BEFORE.

EXCUSE ME, MY EYES
ARE MALFUNCTIONING.

I GOT SOMETHING
IN MINE TOO--

HEY, DO YOU KNOW WHAT
STATION THE EGG RACE IS ON?

I STOLE THE FINISH LINE.
NOW YOU CAN SEE TED WIN.

PLEASE TELL ME
IT'S STILL OPPOSITE DAY.

OH, NO, IT'S ALMOST 3:15.
HE'S NEVER GONNA MAKE IT.

TED, EAT THIS
IN THE NEXT TEN SECONDS.

IT'S COMING
OUT OF YOUR PAY.

YOU GOT A PRETTY NECK,
CARY!

THINK I MIGHT
HAVE TO SQUEEZE IT

WHAT'S ON THAT DRIVE.

I JUST--

LAW? WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

WHAT ARE WE
GONNA DO WITH YOU?

WAIT, WHY IS SHOTBOT
STILL HERE?

IT'S NOT SHOTBOT,
YOU IDIOT, IT'S MY
SMOKING HOT GIRLFRIEND!

I MEAN, YOU KNOW
THAT'S SHOTBOT, RIGHT?

I MEAN, YOU JUST DO.
YOU HAVE TO.

NO, I...
I DON'T ACCEPT THIS.

I MEAN,
THAT IS SO A ROBOT...

YOU GUYS,
JUST TAKE HIM AWAY.

YOU USED ME FOR A STORY!
I TRUSTED YOU!
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.

YEAH, DUCHESS THOUGHT
SHE HAD IT IN THE BAG,

AND THEN, BAM, I TURNED ON
THE BLOOD ELEVATOR.

AND THE SPOOKIEST
GINGERBREAD HOUSE GOES TO...

YOU FORGOT THE CIDER?

YOU MEAN RULED LEETMAS DAY

THEN, YES,
I FORGOT THE CIDER.

NO, NO, NO.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

WE DON'T NEED...

I THOUGHT YOU WERE
GOING TO SHOWER.

AT LEAST WE'RE ALL
HERE TOGETHER, RIGHT?

YOU KNOW WHAT? LET'S JUST
ENJOY THIS PERFECT TURKEY.

I FORGOT THE SALT.
MY BRIAN.

A LOW-SODIUM DIET

INSTEAD OF SALT,
WE COULD USE--

JUST STOP, OKAY?

BRIAN HAS SALT. THAT'S
HOW IT WORKS. THE END.

OH, DO YOU WANT
SOME OF MY BURGER?

I DON'T WANT
ANY OF YOUR BURGER.

THAT'S IT.
IS THAT TOO MUCH?

BUT NO, INSTEAD IT'S,
"COME TO MY RACE, BRIAN.

LET'S HAVE DESSERT
BEFORE DINNER, BRIAN."

CIDER? PIE?
NOT TO DESTROY MY BOOTH,

WHICH I HAVE TO PAY FOR,
BY THE WAY.

I CAN'T AFFORD TUITION. I CAN'T
BE SEEN WITH MY GIRLFRIEND.

- BRIAN!
- AND I DON'T ASK
FOR CRAP...

MAKE THIS MORE ABOUT YOU.
YOU ARE THE MOST SELFISH--

NO, YOU KNOW WHAT?
IT'S FINE. FORGET IT.

YOU'LL BE HEARING
FROM MY LAWYER.

SO... IS HE SERIOUS

'CAUSE I'D BE
IN A LOT OF TROUBLE.

MAY I HAVE YOUR ATTENTION,
PLEASE.

THE RTS TEAM IS PROUD
TO PRESENT FOR YOUR
DUNKING PLEASURE

TAKE ON THE LAW
IN THE ONE GAME

HE CAN'T
CHEAT HIS WAY OUT OF.

ONE GOOD THROW

SO SHOW HIM
HOW YOU FEEL, VGHS!

WAS THIS YOUR
MASTER PLAN, SHANE?

MY MASTER PLAN
IS REAL ESTATE
IN BARBADOS.

IS GONNA DESTROY
THE ONLY EVIDENCE
OF THE TRUTH.

I DON'T KNOW,
I JUST KIND OF
THROW THAT WORD AROUND.

I JUST MADE
A HUNDRED GRAND.

All: DOWN WITH THE LAW!
DOWN WITH THE LAW!

YOU GOING UNDERCOVER
AS A STUDENT WENT MEGAVIRAL.

I GOT MY JOB BACK,
BUT I FAILED.
I DIDN'T GET MY HUMAN STORY.

SCOTT, WHEN THOSE GUARDS
WERE SENT TO DEACTIVATE ME,

IS THAT BECAUSE
YOU CARE ABOUT ME?

YEAH, YOU BIG GREEN GOOF!
NOW, GET IN!

WAIT A SEC,
I KIND OF LIVE IN HERE.

I'M CLEANING IT UP,
ALL RIGHT?

SO... PRETTY EPIC
BLOWUP BACK THERE.
I'M A JERK. I GET IT.

GET UP, 'CAUSE YOU'RE
LYING IN EGGNOG.

BELIEVE ME, MY KID'S

WELL, I MEAN,
FINISH CLEANING THIS UP,

AND CONSIDER THAT
EVEN FOR THE YAMS.

I REALLY SCREWED UP,

I DON'T THINK

YOU MADE A MISTAKE.
YOU'RE A GOOD KID.

NOW, STOP CUE-CUING ABOUT IT
AND GO APOLOGIZE.

I MEAN, CLEAN THIS UP,
BRIAN!

I NEED TO BE ABLE
TO OPEN UP TO YOU.
I JUST...

OKAY, BRIAN, YOU START
BY EATING THAT PIE.

JENNY AND I WILL
TACKLE THE NOG.

HOW ABOUT I
GET YOU SOME SODA

THIS IS WHEN IT HAPPENS!
THIS IS WHEN IT HAPPENS!

HOW DO I GET YOU

WE BOTH KNOW THESE
PYTHONS WON'T HOLD.

IF YOU KNEW I WAS A ROBOT,
YOU'D NEVER LIKE ME.

I DIDN'T LIKE YOU
FOR YOUR SMOKIN' LOOKS.

NOW GET OUT OF HERE
WITH THOSE BEDROOM EYES.

I CAN'T STAND YOU
TO SEE ME LIKE THIS.

NOT UNTIL
I FINISH MY STORY.

YOU IDIOT!
THE WATER WILL KILL YOU!

AND NOW... I'M SORRY,
LAW, BUT BOY LOSES BOT.

MY GOD. THE LAW
DIDN'T CHEAT AFTER ALL.
